ig/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c8133ddacb19aabf1813f92be2924e10aac68c","tid":173513,"uid":739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:15:39.000Z","msg":"乜原來 ubereat  唔係好似 uber 咁自由接單架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00b5a4b1194da82a4e48e0d5ced2eea977b8eeba","tid":173513,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:19:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜原來 ubereat  唔係好似 uber 咁自由接單架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n以前就係，幾時上線都得，而家好煩，遲少少都要同佢報告<br />\n有個師兄試過唔見電話上唔到線，uber夠膽問佢拎報失紙做證據<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98a2ad222e5d8acedfd98bdc6153d98ef5c6d6e7","tid":173513,"uid":11454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T15:22:47.000Z","msg":"要請假？點解唔番老麥， pizza果d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14fc4aa92014cbd814ddd351bf2f07f3466a3ff1","tid":173513,"uid":80396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:03:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要請假？點解唔番老麥， pizza果d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇計，成個OFFICE都係D做實習大學生，九成講<br />\n讀完咩咩管理，就懶醒推出黎管理車手。但坐寫字樓班友九成都未做個揸車呢行，成日諗D鳩屎野。<br />\n<br />\n搞到原本自由自在既工，仲嚴過返政府工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n遲到得多，或者返工時數唔夠報更時數8成，成個星期既時薪就BYE<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098110ed08968613a025acc943f945c069be45b0","tid":173513,"uid":51348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-26T16:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>要請假？點解唔番老麥， pizza果d?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇計，成個OFFICE都係D做實習大學生，九成講<br />\n讀完咩咩管理，就懶醒推出黎管理車手。但坐寫字樓班友九成都未做個揸車呢行，成日諗D鳩屎野。<br />\n<br />\n搞到原本自由自在既工，仲嚴過返政府工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n